-></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul id=\"block-ad220f05-deab-4c06-9152-84ad2d71a994\"><li>Creates a climate that fosters and encourages creative thinking</li><li>Promotes creative processes within and across projects or teams</li><li>Champions breakthrough thinking and creative solutions</li><li>Supports and encourages creativity by enhancing learning and development opportunities</li><li>Acknowledges and rewards creativity</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"column-heading bg-1 fg-white\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group column-heading bg-1 fg-white\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"bg-1 fg-white\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"bg-1 fg-white\">Innovative Thinking</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5,\"className\":\"bg-1 fg-white\"} -->\n<h5 class=\"bg-1 fg-white\">Level 4</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul id=\"block-65c3371e-62b2-48d6-801f-592531422914\"><li>Recognises and takes calculated risks</li><li>Sponsors and coordinates learning from entrepeneurial endeavours and projects</li><li>Anticipates and manages strategic ambiguity and uncertainty</li><li>Develops and coordinates of entrepeneurial projects or initiatives</li><li>Contributes to the development and shaping of innovative business models or plans</li><li>Leads others to realise an entrepeneurial initiative or idea</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"column-heading bg-5 fg-white\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group column-heading bg-5 fg-white\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"bg-5 fg-white\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"bg-5 fg-white\">Communication</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5,\"className\":\"bg-5 fg-white\"} -->\n<h5 class=\"bg-5 fg-white\">Level 5</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul id=\"block-4d398db8-64c4-4f27-9ae3-f456e352ce51\"><li>Promotes knowledge and information development and sharing across the organisation</li><li>Represents the organisation with authority and credibility in public forums and at events</li><li>Develops communication plans to engage internal and external audiences</li><li>Communications directly reinforce the organisation\'s brand and values</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On completion of your course, participants will receive a digital badge outlining the level of achievement attained for each relevant capability.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"w-100 skew-bottom bg-4 p-5\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group w-100 skew-bottom bg-4 p-5\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>What\'s a badge?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Digital badges are a powerful tool for identifying and validating the rich array of people\'s skills, knowledge, accomplishments, and competencies. A digital badge is issued for each course and outlines each capability attained under the program and the level at which each skill is achieved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Badges are embedded with metadata which provides details of what the recipient had to do to earn the badge. The badges are hosted by Credly\'s Acclaim platform which houses each credential and their corresponding data from which individuals can share their achievements, allowing recipients to share their verified credentials with ease.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"skew-top-bottom p-5 bg-1\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group skew-top-bottom p-5 bg-1\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"py-5\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group py-5\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Why you should access your program</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An accredited training course of program is more attractive to individuals who are considering taking your course; the outcomes are transferrable and recognised across different organisations and institutions - it makes the course significantly more valuable. This can be used as a marketing tool for your business or course, as well as a tool to attract candidates and increase employee engagement for your organisation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Verified programs can be used as a currency for career progression. Roles can be anchored to specific achievement levels for key capabilities and individuals can undertake relevant training to ensure their skills are matched to requirements of each role.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":19,\"width\":1024,\"height\":683,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"w-100\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized w-100\"><img src=\"https://veriskills.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/marvin-meyer-SYTO3xs06fU-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->','How it works','','inherit','closed','closed','','116-revision-v1','','','2020-09-25 19:05:43','2020-09-25 09:05:43','',116,'https://veriskills.local/116-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
